text.__SUMMARY__: Prunus clementis is a species of plant in the family Rosaceae. It is found in Sulawesi and the Philippines.
text.Sources: Kalkman, C. (1998). "Prunus clementis". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T37390A10044190. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T37390A10044190.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
